

Session
=======

    $session = new Phifty\Session;
    $session = new Phifty\Session( 'prefix' );

To register a session 'user':

    $session->user = 'user name';

To remove a session:

    $session->remove( 'user' );

To get all variables:

    $args = $session->getAll();

Set all variable expired at ...:

    $session->doExpire( 30 ); // 30 minutes

Get session id:

    $session->getId();

Destroy:

    $session->destroy();
